sc_cat_item.description:
Change up playtime for your aibo with the Dice accessory. Depending on its mood, you can find aibo holding, rolling, throwing, or stacking these dice. As time passes, aibo may even find new ways to play with the dice.
  • Size: 72mm x 72mm x 72mm (approx.)
  • Weight: 49.8g (approx.)
  • Quantity: 2 pieces
  • When playing with dice, please keep it within 50cm in front of aibo.
  • If the surroundings are dark, aibo may not be able to find the dice well.
